version_description:
To make sure you're always getting the best experience we make regular updates to the app. In this release we have:
- Updated eReceipt functionality, so you can view Store details by tapping on the Store name
- Made other minor updates

To make sure you're always getting the best experience we make regular updates to the app. In this release we have:
- Improved navigation so you can access your redemption settings from the ‘my account’ menu.
- Made other minor updates.
To make sure you're always getting the best experience we make regular updates to the app and in this release we have made minor changes.

To make sure you're always getting the best experience we make regular updates to the app. In this release we have:

Refreshed our logo and branding, including how you view your points balance, savings and fuel vouchers.
Added a new tab for your boosters (previously offers).
Added a new tab for your Extras (competitions and giveaways) and Favourites (things you like to buy at great prices).
Updated our dashboard and Discover tab.
Fixed a bug that occurred when boosting (activating).

To make sure you're always getting the best experience we make regular updates to the app. In this release we have:


- Made an update that allows you to filter offers by status.
- Refreshed the look of your offers and other general features.
- Fixed some bugs and technical aspects to improve your overall experience.
